{"tid":2248061,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"LISA教螃蟹舞、計程車舞連2天登熱搜！全昭旻照學「像酒醉招車」","createTime":"2020-10-18T10:19:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T15:03:51.000Z","uid":16659,"like":7,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"aac0b1ec25be1b6de9db7660c31d89ebe96e5c76","tid":2248061,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T10:19:02.000Z","msg":"南韓女團BLACKPINK宣傳期大舉參加綜藝節目錄影，一連上了《認識的哥哥》與《Running Man》，讓LISA與Jennie名字連續兩天登上韓網熱搜！尤其LISA教家鄉泰國熱門夯舞「螃蟹舞」與「計程車舞」，全昭旻照樣學卻像酒醉大媽招車，笑翻全場！<br />\n<br />\n昨（17）日《認識的哥哥》先公開BLACKPINK特輯，其中以跳舞讓眾人讚嘆的LISA，先示範了一段超帥氣的舞蹈後，接下來介紹節目班底現在泰國最流行的一種舞蹈，就叫「螃蟹舞」，這段舞蹈的重點是一邊跳，一邊要無表情，才能展現這舞的精隨。<br />\n<br />\n隨著泰文音樂一下，LISA先是手比YA的動作但手掌往下，接著臀部隨著節奏往前頂，手部還可以變換姿勢變成手肘向前，簡單的動作讓一旁《認識的哥哥》班底一學就會，甚至在後面玩遊戲搶答時，一興奮就把螃蟹舞拿出來跳，完全抓到舞蹈精髓！<br />\n<br />\n不僅如此，今（18）日的《Running Man》特輯嘉賓也是BLACKPINK，這回LISA也搬出之前秀過的泰式招計程車舞，從一開始就隨著節奏踏步搖晃，突然看見遠方有計程車，她手張開作出招車動作，完美呈現泰舞神韻。下一秒全昭旻被拱照跳，彷彿酒醉招車的模樣笑翻眾人。<br />\n<br />\n因為活躍的綜藝表現，LISA連續兩天登上南韓最大搜尋引擎Naver的熱搜關鍵字前5名，另外「Jennie」、「Jennie年紀」、「BLACKPINK年紀」等也登上熱搜排行榜。<br />\n▼LISA教泰國最新螃蟹舞。（影片來源：YouTube 아는형님 Knowingbros）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=01iz9kmvbxg&amp;feature=emb_title\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D01iz9kmvbxg%26feature%3Demb_title&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1a7P2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=f6d2451e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=01iz9kmvbxg&amp;feature=emb_title</a>"},{"pid":"1df068b3cbed89062414c52502a74c0f7fe2e6ea","tid":2248061,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T10:19:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5212/d5212359.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5212%2Fd5212359.jpg&h=a5c9b133&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲LISA在《認識的哥哥》先教螃蟹舞。（圖／翻攝自YouTube／아는형님 Knowingbros）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5212/d5212355.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5212%2Fd5212355.jpg&h=f266a47c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼LISA示範計程車舞，但全昭旻一跳卻變樣。（圖／翻攝自YouTube／런닝맨 - 스브스 공식 채널）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5212/d5212356.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5212%2Fd5212356.jpg&h=7ce9a39f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f0220068cbf6ea35c7fca566f9dfce5721bea5fe","tid":2248061,"uid":93096,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T10:20:22.000Z","msg":"好撚完美<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64a44c09781671b2a5556764ce01629cc5bf6110","tid":2248061,"uid":76563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T10:21:00.000Z","msg":"以為係熱咖啡"},{"pid":"dc663b16f997b4ac572233456f81ddfd26a2312b","tid":2248061,"uid":16659,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T10:21:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-DI0XtL17LEY/X4v5pvlVz8I/AAAAAAACCLg/0wo7WPovqYk0jZ8UTJmvpV1hrbLGINrhwCLcBGAsYHQ/s640/SmartSelect_20201018-170818_wavve.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-DI0XtL17LEY%2FX4v5pvlVz8I%2FAAAAAAACCLg%2F0wo7WPovqYk0jZ8UTJmvpV1hrbLGINrhwCLcBGAsYHQ%2Fs640%2FSmartSelect_20201018-170818_wavve.gif&h=e0d62227&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-deteLaK4_yM/X4v5pr0HS3I/AAAAAAACCLk/Ww_EPa7AEbkS4TF0zOxrRLGYm6rM-C7fQCLcBGAsYHQ/s640/SmartSelect_20201018-170835_wavve.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-deteLaK4_yM%2FX4v5pr0HS3I%2FAAAAAAACCLk%2FWw_EPa7AEbkS4TF0zOxrRLGYm6rM-C7fQCLcBGAsYHQ%2Fs640%2FSmartSelect_20201018-170835_wavve.gif&h=f5cd8e7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-vfcgeTXkyPY/X4v5p3ttRFI/AAAAAAACCLo/GtaRAxiMrccPdPnET0LmAQ63tTAKPg_YgCLcBGAsYHQ/s640/SmartSelect_20201018-170848_wavve.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.